com.centurylink.mdw.microservice

Class MicroserviceInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.centurylink.mdw.microservice.MicroserviceInstance
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.limberest.json.Jsonable

    public class MicroserviceInstance
extends java.lang.Object
implements Jsonable
    Represents a microservice's invocations and updates for one process instance. Invocations will always be non-null (empty if none), whereas updates can be null.
